Happy New Music Friday, we have some great new releases this week!

Norwegian duo KREAM returns with their signature sound in "Arrival", delivering a cosmic journey through melodic tech-house with futuristic soundscapes. Marten Hørger brings us "No Ecstasy Love", a bass house anthem that blends nostalgic rave elements with contemporary production. Meanwhile, Arguello teams up with Naty Botero for "TKM", a vibrant house track infused with Latin rhythms perfect for summer dancefloors. 


Check all of our new releases here: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLx_tr69QV8CBSAtVsMSME8IoAe3lDxMFQ&si=JUwYTFVnR-DEch0h
